<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.7">
<l>karuntaṇ kaṭalum malaiyu mulakum</l>
<l>aruntu maṭika ḷamaru mūrpōl</l>
<l>peruntaṇ mullaip piḷḷai yōṭik</l>
<l>kuruntan taḻuvuṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where [new] shoots of long, cool jasmine [vines],</l>
<l>Spreading, entwine [around] the kuruntu [trees],</l>
<l>It seems, is the city where abides the lord who contains</l>
<l>The earth, mountains, and dark, cool sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
